subject: Hockey, Ice
Playoff Games
Stanley Cup
lead_paragraph: Ryan Getzlaf and Jakob Silfverberg scored to lead the Anaheim Ducks to a 2-1 victory at the Arizona Coyotes in their regular-season finale on Saturday night.
